            <p>
               The text follows the edition of J. Ramayya Pantulu in <bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:RamayyaPantulu1948_01"/><citedRange unit="page">339</citedRange><citedRange unit="item">627</citedRange></bibl> in absence of a picture.
