        <div type="bibliography">
	<p>
              The inscription was noted in A. R. No. 307 of 1922 <!-- has to be adjusted to the @target --> and first published by J. Ramayya Pantulu in <bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:RamayyaPantulu1948_01"/><citedRange unit="page">339</citedRange><citedRange unit="item">627</citedRange></bibl> with few metadata and without translation.
